text: Fleetwood Town Football Club is an English professional football club from Fleetwood, Lancashire. They currently play in League One, the third level of football in England. They are nicknamed 'The Fishermen' or ‘The Cods’ due to Fleetwood being a coastal town. Their home stadium is Highbury Stadium. The stadium can hold 5,327 fans.
